title: I cannot access my contacts, nor my phone app. Please help, I cannot call from my phone
content:
When I open my "phone" app, everything is blank, as if I have no contacts, and shortly after that, pop up message shows up saying the "phone" app is not responding. When I try to call using my "phone" app, I can put in the numbers, but the call button is not showing. 

When I open my contact app, it's just keeps loading. and show none of my contacts
